There are multiple copies of this text in the Drepung dKar chag, but the title does not refer to a stod or smad cha. 
#22085; #22359; Nang475-2459 (in 'Bras spungs pho brang gzim chung gi rje lam rim pa'i dpe mdzod dkar chag); and Nang234-839 (in 'Bras spungs sgo mang grwa tshang gi dpe mdzod dkar chag) all appear to be the same version of this text; 430 folios in each and all written in shing dpar;
#Nang101-281 (in 'Bras spungs pho brang gzim chung gi rje lam rim pa'i dpe mdzod dkar chag) is also written in shing dpar; 246 folios; size 58 x 10;
#Nang341-1822 (in 'Bras spungs pho brang gzim chung gi rje lam rim pa'i dpe mdzod dkar chag) is also written in shing dpar; 511 folios; size 64 x 12

